00:13:47,279 --> 00:13:50,399
na Salonu roku 1831 ministerstvo

269
00:13:50,399 --> 00:13:52,980
vnitra zakoupí Svobodu pro

270
00:13:52,980 --> 00:13:55,079
Lucemburské muzeum

